'''Domain Vorrik''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. A notable member of Domain Vorrik was [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[B'shith Vorrik]]. During the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], Domain Vorrik's vessels were part of the flotilla sent to attack [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]].

